item.title: ::ipban ::banuser
item.dc:creator: @Punkzombie Punkzombie
item.description:
@Punkzombie wrote:

most java servers (including rsps) are case sensitive at times… this means if player name is Matt and you do “::banuser matt” than it would not work but if you did “::banuser Matt” it would work
